Sentencas: The aim of the present work is to perform preliminary investigations on samples from the La-Sr-Ti-O system.
Titulo: Synthesis and study of compositions of the La-Sr-Ti-O system for SOFCs anode development

Sentencas: The following compositions: La1-x,SrxTiO3 (x = 0.5; 0.6; 0.7; 0.8) have been the focus of a study as materials with a possible application as alternative anodes for solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Synthesis and study of compositions of the La-Sr-Ti-O system for SOFCs anode development

Sentencas: it was established that all the compositions possess a well defined structure, appropriate for SOFCs anode application.
Titulo: Synthesis and study of compositions of the La-Sr-Ti-O system for SOFCs anode development

Sentencas: From the conductivity data and impedance measurements, it was found that the material La0.5Sr0.5TiO3 demonstrates good ionic conductivity and could be used as a basic phase for producing composite anodes for SOFCs.
Titulo: Synthesis and study of compositions of the La-Sr-Ti-O system for SOFCs anode development
